OL,3,CInland surfing lake The Wave closes
OL,4,Csuddenly amid 'financial difficulties'
OL,6,FA popular inland surfing lake on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of Bristol has closed
OL,8,Fsuddenly.
OL,10,FIn a statement on social media on
OL,11,FWednesday 25 June, The Wave said: "Due
OL,12,Fto unforeseen circumstances The Wave
OL,13,Fwill be closed tomorrow, Thursday 26th
OL,14,FJune.
OL,16,F"All customers with surf bookings have
OL,17,Fbeen contacted by e-mail with further
OL,18,Finformation."
OL,20,FThe Wave's website is also out of
OL,21,Faction.
