OL,3,CInland surfing lake The Wave closes
OL,4,Csuddenly amid 'financial difficulties'
OL,6,FThe attraction in Easter Compton is an
OL,7,Finland surfing lake that has welcomed
OL,8,Fmore than 400,000 visitors since
OL,9,Fopening in 2019.
OL,11,FIn a statement majority owners
OL,12,FSullivan Street Partners said the
OL,13,Fdecision came as a result of a
OL,14,F"financial technicality".
OL,16,F"It is with great sadness that we
OL,17,Fannounce the closure of The Wave
OL,18,FBristol, the UK's first inland surf
OL,19,Fdestination and a much-loved community
OL,20,Fasset", the statement said.
