OL,3,CInland surfing lake The Wave closes
OL,4,Csuddenly amid 'financial difficulties'
OL,6,F"This decision has not been driven by
OL,7,Foperational failure or lack of
OL,8,Fcustomer demand`but for a financial
OL,9,Ftechnicality completely unrelated to
OL,10,FSullivan Street Partners, which owns a
OL,11,Fmajority stake in the business.
OL,13,F"The Wave Group, owners of the surf
OL,14,Fpark in Bristol, has lined up a
OL,15,Frefinancing alongside its exciting
OL,16,FLondon developments, which would see
OL,17,Fall creditors repaid in full within a
OL,18,Fweek and is offering to continue to
OL,19,Foperate the park."
