OL,6,FThe statement went on to say: "The
OL,7,FWave Group team apologises
OL,8,Funreservedly for any upset caused and
OL,9,Fis doing its best to ensure the
OL,10,Fsituation can be remedied."
OL,12,FA national charity event - Cerebra's
OL,13,FRelay Your Way - was due to take place
OL,14,Fat the site today, 26 June, as part of
OL,15,Fit's ongoing tour from Glasgow to
OL,16,FWindsor.
