OL,6,FThe Wave owners said previously it was
OL,7,Fan "absolute honour" to be selected to
OL,8,Ftake part.
OL,10,FThe Wave was England's first surfing
OL,11,Flake, built in 2019. It cost #25
OL,12,Fmillion to build and took nine years
OL,13,Fto complete. 26 million litres of
OL,14,Fwater were needed to fill the lake.
